### How to keep output fresh

How do not let the LLM to repeat themselves?

1. Presence penalty: Fixed penalty to tokens that were used before
2. Frequency penalty: Dcaling penalty, the more you use it the less likely it will be used in the future

These penalties are applied early in the token selection process..they act as simple reminders not to develop bad habits


